<h2>To All Wine Lovers</h2>

<div class="row">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="col-sm-5">
            
                <p>
                    Jiu Zhuang (meaning wine merchant) is delicated to those lovers of wine who would like to share their experiences and comments.
                </p>
                <p>
                    If you have the wines you like, why not share with others and let us all know their Names, Grapes,
                    Regions and Countries or even upload an image link from the internet, so that we can watch out
                    for the wines you recommend.
                </p>

                <h4>Alias</h4>
                <p>
                    Due to user authentication is not part of the scope for this project. There is no personal sign up but why
                    don't you have a look at the different aliases and choose one and add your comments to the wines.
                </p>
            </div>
        

        <div class="col-sm-4"></div>
                
        <div class="col-sm-3">           
                <h4>Wine</h4>
                <span>
                    In the Wine section, you can look at the wine list use <strong>Edit </strong>to change the wine details
                    , <strong>Display </strong>to look at the details in full. Also, within the detail screen you can use
                    <strong>Create </strong>to add comments of your own.
                </span>
            
            </div>        
    </div>
